---
title: Sweet and Sour Tofu with cashew and coriander topped jasmine rice
description: The sauce that coats the tofu and veg in this recipe is slightly sweet with just the right amount of tanginess. The coriander and cashew topping adds crunch and freshness to an already impressive dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R21_W14_IE_IECFQV14265-3_Main__3high-79abeaf3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/659828206b4bf2cf1c67ebf4.pdf
course: main course
servings: 2
time required: 25 minutes
author: HelloFresh
source: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipes/sweet-and-sour-tofu-659828206b4bf2cf1c67ebf4
